title: Untitled
description: dynamically-posed, abstracted figure with PL arm outstretched, PR arm down with hand as support; legs apart with shorter PR leg stretched out in front and longer PL leg bent at knee out to the side; flat face; incised slit eyes; open mouth; carved of petrified whale bone, with sponge-appearing, cellular areas and more solid areas; hole on top of PL knee; bone is cream colored, tan and brown
